questions: What is the capability of ThamesThrive to fetch contact information from ActiveCampaign?
How to fetch ActiveCampaign contact info using ThamesThrive?
What is the plugin used to fetch contact information from ActiveCampaign using ThamesThrive?
answer:
# Can ThamesThrive fetch contact information from ActiveCampaign based on the given email address?
Yes, ThamesThrive can fetch ActiveCampaign contact info based on the given email address using the "Fetch contact" plugin
